```plantuml
@startuml gapfish_deployer
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "depctl CLI" as CLI #lightgrey

rectangle "Kubernetes Cluster" as KubeCluster #aliceblue {
  rectangle "Deployment" as Deployment
  rectangle "Service" as Service
  rectangle "ConfigMap/Secret" as ConfigMapSecret
}

rectangle "gapfish_deployer" as Deployer #lightyellow {
  rectangle "EventStreamLogger" as EventLogger
  rectangle "Plugin System" as PluginSystem
  rectangle "Configuration Manager" as ConfigManager
  rectangle "Docker Image Builder" as DockerBuilder
}

rectangle "External API" as ExternalAPI #lightsteelblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> CLI : interact with

CLI --> Deployer : trigger deployment\ncheck status\nmanage canary releases
Deployer --> KubeCluster : apply modified\nresource definitions
Deployer --> EventLogger : log deployment\nprogress and status

Deployer --> PluginSystem : load and execute\nconfigured plugins
Deployer --> DockerBuilder : build Docker images\nwith correct tags
Deployer <-> ConfigManager : manage configurations\nand environment variables

EventLogger --> PluginSystem : notify subscribers\non specific events

Deployer <-> ExternalAPI : communicate with external\nservices (e.g., Bugsnag)
@enduml
```